            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/374456-kerri-anne?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/374456-kerri-anne?shelf=running-with-the-wolves">running-with-the-wolves</a>, 
